&lt;li&gt;Identify performance degradation, intent gaps, hallucination, model drift, and guardrail failures across Zendesk AI, chatbots, ticketbots, and automation workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the incident response process for AI quality issues — when performance degrades or a guardrail fails, you triage, escalate, and drive resolution with a clear post-mortem&lt;/li&gt;
