&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted strategic advisor to the leadership team on brand reputation, public positioning, and narrative development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage relationships with external PR agencies; collaborate to shape press strategy, identify and prioritize opportunities, and brief them on launches, company news and proactive storylines.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
